-- Taiwan to Tax Idle Land Next Year to Curb Speculators, Economic Daily Says
-- B y   T i m   C u l p a n
-- 2010-10-10T22:36:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-10/taiwan-to-tax-idle-land-next-year-to-curb-speculators-economic-daily-says.html
Taiwan’s Ministry of Finance plans
to begin taxing idle land from next year at a rate of at least 1
percent of the property’s value to curb speculation, the
Economic Daily News reported today, without saying where it got
the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rebecca Evans at 
 revans6@bloomberg.net  